thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Roseann

author: Roseann
title: Roseann
text: Rubberstamp champ's online ordering process is so easy and quick. Pick the stamp you want, pick the wording for your stamp, pick the letterstyle and color and you are done. Communication regarding your order is swift and shipping is fast, well packaged and perfect every time. Its my go to place when I need a stamp!
